## Get records

```js

// Get the records from a specific view. Returns the first page of records by default
datasheet.records.query({ viewId: "{{ viewId }}"}).then(response => {
  if (response.success) {
    console.log(response.data);
  } else {
    console.error(response);
  }
});

```

